- \frac{n}{52!} \approx \log 0.1 \approx -2.30.
n \approx 2.30 \cdot 52! \approx 2.30 \cdot \sqrt{106\pi} \left( \frac{52}{e} \right)^{52} \approx 1.87 \times 10^{68}
